Invocation Name: redlands guide
des: Redlands is full of local attractions that appeal to people of all ages. This skill will provide you with a list of must-do activities and must-see areas that will guarantee you a worthwhile trip to the Jewel of the Inland Empire. This skill will continuously updated with more local food spots and attractions as Redlands continues to develop and introduce new activities to the local scene.
